divs: Sighting DetailsSunday afternoon on a hilltop park in northeast Seattle, walking dog. Orange disk slowly banking away. Sorry, only had a cell camera in the car. Wonder if it an airplane (see many in ther sky near here) but it was an odd orange color.
Summary: Looked disc shaped, just gradually banked away, was it an airplane?
